You're the type to make strange movements, I see.

367
00:28:19,894 --> 00:28:24,094
うふふ。でも今日はちょっと大人しくね、お話します。
Hehe. But today I'll talk a bit more calmly.

368
00:28:24,094 --> 00:28:28,594
