...but Toko-san accepted it.

526
00:35:34,117 --> 00:35:35,617
いや、それはするでしょ
Well, of course I would.

527
00:35:35,617 --> 00:35:38,617
そんなだだってせっかくこれ一番お芋大きいですって選んでくれたら
Since you went to the trouble of picking the biggest one for me...

528
00:35:38,617 --> 00:35:41,617
「じゃあこれ！」って
...I'm like, "Then I'll take this one!"

529
00:35:41,617 --> 00:35:44,317
